This project contains the pseudo thread files.

The threading files are in the com.piematrix.pseudoThreader package.
These files are under the MIT license: http://www.opensource.org/licenses/mit-license.php.

Based on code from http://blogs.adobe.com/aharui/2008/01/threads_in_actionscript_3.html.

The com.piematrix.test.PseudoThreadTest.mxml file contains examples on how to use the threader.

